				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/D%E1%BB%AF-H%C3%A0-N%E1%BB%99i-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-S%C6%A1n-T%C3%A2y-tam-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-hoan-%E1%BA%A9m-t%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0-ho%E1%BA%A1/poem--ME8xYVde9vcVd48Xl4YCg">Dữ Hà Nội Bắc Ninh Sơn Tây tam đại đốc hoan ẩm tức tịch thư hoạ - 與河内北寧山西三大督歡飲卽席書和</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C4%83ng-V%C3%A2n-H%C3%A0n/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-luy%E1%BA%BFn-hoa-Qu%C3%A1-v%C5%A9-xu%C3%A2n-ba-ph%C3%B9-%C3%A1p-l%E1%BB%A5c/poem-fXtdIyJ_tk_FcLgIS7O3_A">Điệp luyến hoa (Quá vũ xuân ba phù áp lục) - 蝶戀花（過雨春波浮鴨綠）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C4%83ng-V%C3%A2n-H%C3%A0n/author-wKJv1CZbWt0UhuCagXrD5w">Lăng Vân Hàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/%C4%90o%E1%BA%A1n-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C3%A2n-thanh-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-_gpeIIoa4A7Zm2Ip1UR2lA">Đoạn trường tân thanh đề từ - 斷腸新聲題辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/author-_a5NZkjlUmxBDVuBs6LQJg">Phạm Quý Thích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Nam-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-ho%C3%A0i-T%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/poem-oXdUVeB0_uuP6YS2lwYHpQ">Hạ nhật Nam Đình hoài Tân Đại - 夏日南亭懷辛大</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/H%E1%BB%99i-ch%C3%A2n-thi/poem-LeoeJ0FsHz3zUPXXvFeE_g">Hội chân thi - 會真詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-V%E1%BA%ADn/K%C3%BD-Ho%C3%A0i-